section.rating
  .container
    .rating__content
      .rating__card
        picture.rating__element-top
          source(srcset="./assets/images/element/element-1.webp" type="image/webp")
          img(src="./assets/images/element/element-1.png" alt="element-1")
        h3.rating__card-title What our customers are saying
        .rating__card-content
          .rating__card-person
            .rating__card-person-img
              img(src="./assets/icons/rating/person-icon.svg" alt="img-person-rating")
            .rating__card-person-name
              h4 Ak
              p Abc ltd
          .rating__card-describing
            | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa.
      picture.rating__element-bottom
        source(srcset="./assets/images/element/element-1.webp" type="image/webp")
        img(src="./assets/images/element/element-1.png" alt="element-1")
      .rating__control
        a.rating__control-directional(href='#' aria-label="Previous")
          i.rating__control-icon.fa-solid.fa-left-long
        ul.rating__control-list
          li.rating__control-item
            a#element-focus(href='#' aria-label="Page 1")
          li.rating__control-item
            a(href='#' aria-label="Page 2")
          li.rating__control-item
            a(href='#' aria-label="Page 3")
          li.rating__control-item
            a(href='#' aria-label="Page 4")
        a.rating__control-directional(href='#' aria-label="Next")
          i.rating__control-icon.fa-solid.fa-right-long
